title: Jurassic World Toys Camp Cretaceous Sound Strike Cryolophosaurus Medium-size Dinosaur Figure, Strike Action, Sounds, Movable Joints, Ages 4 Years Old & Up
features: This medium-sized Jurassic World Sound Strike dinosaur action figure is inspired by the Jurassic World: Camp Cretaceous animated series!
Activate the "Primal Attack" feature by moving the tail side to side or up and down for strike action (move both at the same time for realistic, animated movement).

Realistic sculpting, movable joints, authentic color and texture makes the figure come alive!

description: Get ready for more thrills and adventure with Jurassic World! This medium-size Sound Strike dinosaur is inspired by the Jurassic World: Camp Cretaceous animated series and captures the ultimate dinosaur battle action! This Sound Strike dinosaur action figure features the "Primal Attack" feature which enables kids to control the battle play by either moving the tail on the figure from side to side or up and down for strike action! Make both moves at the same time for realistic, animated movement! Plus, any of the movements activate realistic dinosaur sounds for the total dinosaur battle experience! This Sound Strike dinosaur action figure also features authentic sculpting, movable joints and realistic color and texture. Colors and decorations may vary. Makes a great gift for ages 4 years old and up especially fans of the Jurassic World, dinosaurs and action play! For more dinosaur fun, download the Jurassic World Facts app (Android and iOS) to scan and watch your dinosaur come to life, zoom in on dinosaurs up close, hear dinosaur roars, learn fun dinosaur facts and more!
